<h1 id="web-mapping">Web Mapping</h1>

<p>Web mapping takes cartography beyond static maps.  Today, we‚Äôll use a Python package called [gollium]http://python-visualization.github.io/folium/ which allows us to create dynamic, interactive webmaps that can be embedded in webpages.  Folium will ‚Äútranslate‚Äù our python commands into Javascrpt and create <a href="https://leafletjs.com/">leaflet</a> maps.  Leaflet is a javascript   Follium is already installed, so we don‚Äôt have any more steps to do here!</p>

